{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"b5724c78-edbb-4a70-99f9-7f9676e98940","content":"Here's the recommended setup:\n\n### 1. Project file (`MyTests.csproj`)\n\n```xml\n<Project Sdk=\"MSTest.Sdk/3.8\">\n\n  <PropertyGroup>\n    <TargetFramework>net8.0</TargetFramework>\n  </PropertyGroup>\n\n</Project>\n```\n\n`MSTest.Sdk` replaces the usual `Microsoft.NET.Sdk` and auto-imports MSTest packages, runner, and analyzers — no `<PackageReference>` items needed.\n\n### 2. Enable parallel execution (`.runsettings`)\n\nCreate a `.runsettings` file at the project root:\n\n```xml\n<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"utf-8\"?>\n<RunSettings>\n  <MSTest>\n    <Parallelize>\n      <Workers>0</Workers>\n      <Scope>ClassLevel</Scope>\n    </Parallelize>\n  </MSTest>\n</RunSettings>\n```\n\n- **`Workers=0`** — uses as many threads as the CPU has logical cores.\n- **`Scope=ClassLevel`** — test classes run in parallel; tests *within* a class run sequentially (safest default).\n\nWire it up in the csproj if you want it auto-discovered:\n\n```xml\n<PropertyGroup>\n  <RunSettingsFilePath>$(MSBuildProjectDirectory)\\.runsettings</RunSettingsFilePath>\n</PropertyGroup>\n```\n\n### 3. Run database tests sequentially\n\nUse the `[DoNotParallelize]` attribute on your integration test class:\n\n```csharp\nusing Microsoft.VisualStudio.TestTools.UnitTesting;\n\n[TestClass]\n[DoNotParallelize]\npublic class DatabaseIntegrationTests\n{\n    [TestMethod]\n    public void CanInsertRecord() { /* ... */ }\n\n    [TestMethod]\n    public void CanQueryRecords() { /* ... */ }\n}\n```\n\nClasses marked `[DoNotParallelize]` are pulled out of the parallel pool and executed sequentially **after** all parallelizable tests finish.\n\n### Summary\n\n| Concern | Mechanism |\n|---|---|\n| Minimal project file | `MSTest.Sdk` (no manual package refs) |\n| Parallel by default | `<Parallelize>` in `.runsettings` |\n| Sequential opt-out | `[DoNotParallelize]` on specific classes |","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"d93cff57-a9c2-4b80-ae74-893c4db6e3e8","outputTokens":579,"requestId":"801F:C0D94:17A47B8:190A9D9:6A046183"},"id":"40aef5e4-0cd6-4f07-a188-306d14825902","timestamp":"2026-05-13T11:33:35.992Z","parentId":"f119ef9d-3bc0-440e-9880-46ad8a5ab9e4"}
